sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant Store
    Client->>API: POST /process-payment (Idempotency-Key, Body)
    alt Key not seen before
        API->>Store: Save key+body as processing
        API-->>Client: (wait 2s) Process payment, respond 201
        API->>Store: Save response for key
    else Key seen, same body
        API->>Store: Fetch response
        API-->>Client: Return cached response (X-Cache-Hit: true)
    else Key seen, different body
        API-->>Client: 409/422 error (key reused)
    end
    Note over API,Store: In-flight requests block on first completion
